# Profile-based workflow
#
# Do not edit this file directly. Instead:
#   1. Copy .env.owner.example → .env.owner  and fill in your owner account.
#   2. Copy .env.buyer.example → .env.buyer  and fill in your buyer account.
#   3. Run `pnpm env:owner` or `pnpm env:buyer` to activate a profile.
#
# To split an existing single-account .env into profiles:
#   pnpm env:bootstrap
#
# To check the currently active profile:
#   pnpm env:status
